Support for Ford SYNC AppLink!
-Featuring voice-activated controls, providing an easy to use and safe Rhapsody listening experience
-Connect via Bluetooth
-Listen and customize your top 9 playlists 
-Listen to select Genre by name 
-Play Artist radio from current track 
-Save current playing track to Favorites
-Offline mode for downloaded tracks
-Works with select Ford Models http://www.ford.com/technology/
 
